  "identifier": "ggsegHO",
  "description": "Harvard-Oxford cortical and subcortical atlases for the 'ggseg' ecosystem. Includes the original Harvard-Oxford atlas (48 cortical regions, 17 subcortical structures) and the Harvard-Oxford Atlas 2.0 (49 cortical regions, 32 subcortical structures from 200 HCP subjects). All atlases are provided as 'ggseg_atlas' objects with 2D polygon and 3D mesh geometry.",
